{"tid":1723583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭係唯一做到核彈都唔割既人","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:42:58.000Z","uid":144819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"311dbb08092ca4e628d43d835262f862fc54aefb","tid":1723583,"uid":144819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:34:55.000Z","msg":"無論popo 做左d咩<br />\n死都幫佢兜 連搵人祭旗都唔做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁先至係真正核彈都唔割既表現</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地呢？日日都窩裡鬥<br />\n<br />\n講真成場運動好多野我都唔同意<br />\n但每個人都有唔同諗法 我地要做既係討論 唔係互屌<br />\n中大裡面有d人既做法係唔好 我地應該嘗試制止 但唔係割席 鬧佢地出賣 捉鬼<br />\n中大校長成篇野鬧部份黑衣唔鬧popo 既做法都好差 但我地都唔應該分化 錯哂Focus<br />\n<br />\n淺藍既人拉唔到黃都唔好將佢推到去深藍<br />\n淺黃既人那怕只係小小黃 都應該用鼓勵既方式令佢更黃 而唔係下下屌到佢唔想再幫我地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做法只可討論 不可割席<br />\n槍口一致對外 大家既敵人只有一個</span></span>"},{"pid":"3cfe40d5a150192188ddbc2b59d460159d559dd8","tid":1723583,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:36:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=37bd6e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSenator Scott 幫香港人出聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senrickscott/status/1195147582609252353?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=a6d697ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&h=37d03fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senrickscott/stat